<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure7>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Catherinum cf. novaezelandiae (Hoek, 1883). Specimen CCZ _ 185: A in situ photograph B right C left lateral views. Scale bars: 1 cm (A); 1 mm (B, C). Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A), Hosie (B, C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716333" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure8>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Rooted Bayesian phylogeny of Actiniaria. Concatenated (12 S, 16 S, 18 S, 28 S, COI, and COX 3) BEAST median consensus tree with posterior probability (PP) and bootstrap (BS) values indicated. Only values of PP> 0.70 and BS> 50 are shown, with values of PP> 0.95 and BS> 90 indicated with a circle. Nodes not recovered on the RAxML tree are indicated with a hyphen. Sequences generated in this study are highlighted in violet." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716334" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure9>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Metridioidea stet. CCZ _ 072 A oral B lateral views. Scale bars: 5 mm (A, B). Image attribution: Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (A, B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716335" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Trianguloscalpellum gigas (Hoek, 1883). Specimen CCZ _ 074: A in situ photograph, attached to a glass sponge stalk B left C and right lateral views. Scale bars: 5 cm (A); 1 mm (B, C). Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A), Hosie (B, C). Arrows indicate position of T. gigas (specimen CCZ _ 074; lower, yellow) and Catherinum cf. albatrossianum (specimen CCZ _ 073; upper, green)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716331" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Metridioidea stet. CCZ _ 154 A in situ image B specimen before preservation. Scale bars: A, B 1 cm. Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A), Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716336" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Metridioidea stet. CCZ _ 164 A in situ image of specimen CCZ _ 164 B detail of oral disc C lateral view of specimen. Scale bars: 2 cm (A); 2 mm (B); 5 mm (C). Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A), Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (B, C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716337" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure12>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Actinostolidae stet. CCZ _ 183 A specimen attached to nodule B close-up of specimen. Scale bars: 1 cm (A), 2 mm (B). Image attribution: Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (A, B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716338" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure13>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Actinostolidae stet. CCZ _ 202 A in situ image B detail of specimen. Scale bars: 1 cm (A); 1 mm (B). Image attributions: Durden and Smith (A), Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (B)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716339" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

